reviews.review_text: AWESOME........ This was my first show....   front row centre, and a SHAKEDOWN..........  What A Night !!!!!

Fantastic AUD This is a great recording of one of my favorite shows.  While I will always love the DSBD, this recording really is worth having as well.  The energy of the crowd is amazing. Thanks to the taper and uploader!

Good This was a fine show, my first in Canada. A cop outside gave me a dollar for a hot dog. You can't really beat that. Well-played, tight, and a great setlist. My friend traded the latest Deadbase for a ticket within 3 minutes of arriving at the lot, and I barely got in. Tickets were hard to come by.
Thank You!    Finally a great sounding source.  This was probably one heaviest shows ever!   Oh what a trip.
